[30;1m131 | [0m[35m        # A small trick to exclude private properties. Properties are serialized by pydantic,[0m

[30;1m135 | [0m[35m            {field for field in self.__dict__ if field.startswith("_") and not field == "__root__"},[0m

[30;1m18 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m19 | [0m[35mThe FileIO abstraction includes a subset of full filesystem implementations. Specifically,[0m
[30;1m20 | [0m[35mIceberg needs to read or write a file at a given location (as a seekable stream), as well[0m
[30;1m21 | [0m[35mas check if a file exists. An implementation of the FileIO abstract base class is responsible[0m
